{"tid":1912384,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手養貓求救","createTime":"2020-03-06T04:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T11:13:51.000Z","uid":289104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a86f99bf49ec9b8eb4c5940b31cc051429f9662d","tid":1912384,"uid":289104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n隻貓仲有幾日足3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前因為生貓癬所以放籠入面養<br />\n每日都會放佢出嚟玩陣<br />\n佢而家已經好番 但日日都又張牙又舞爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有陣會長期開疾走咁係屋企跑嚟跑去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲成日咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日咬到我見晒紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩方法令佢唔好咁癲 同埋唔好成日咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab606a40d960cb7ca78ac85af398d883b74a9e1","tid":1912384,"uid":250511,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"你試下喺籠入面住3個月先講嘢啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"ffb504fdac85e9e0b0eda5071e63ec850fe84a5d","tid":1912384,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"e4ec36c321cb143bae958fb76d2dd9871fa566cb","tid":1912384,"uid":253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:38:03.000Z","msg":"3個月咁多電量係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爪可以剪甲 但牙就唔好比佢慣左咬奴才手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5d82155854633cc4384a70c5a3a5cb2ff95397","tid":1912384,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"慢慢黎啦"},{"pid":"0f5b130527232ce17c03c8552240505201f44e82","tid":1912384,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"有冇貓貓圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcfd0130cdf024e391f9b8600e0d046e4fea958","tid":1912384,"uid":289104,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7ab606a40d960cb7ca78ac85af398d883b74a9e1","tid":1912384,"uid":250511,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"你試下喺籠入面住3個月先講嘢啦 屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"其實佢兩個月我先接佢番嚟<br />\n我養左佢一個月 <br />\n頭半個月都係放出嚟養<br />\n結果佢生癬惹到我同女友成身都係<br />\n所以先改左放佢入籠養每日放佢出嚟一陣<br />\n無必要未問清楚就搵伯母 伯母唔得閒個個都應酬"},{"pid":"daccf93342db7fac88d2f5da382de334453eb9b0","tid":1912384,"uid":5258,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"跑黎跑去係放電姐 同埋幼貓有活力啲<br />\n反而咬人真係要教<br />\n唔好拎手指同佢玩 改用玩具/𢭃貓棒<br />\n分散佢注意力<br />\n被咬時要大叫 等佢知道對方會痛"},{"pid":"c988a2b325a8ee38291973dc7e12a8e1a33bf346","tid":1912384,"uid":289104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4ec36c321cb143bae958fb76d2dd9871fa566cb","tid":1912384,"uid":253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:38:03.000Z","msg":"3個月咁多電量係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爪可以剪甲 但牙就唔好比佢慣左咬奴才手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:41:30.000Z","msg":"如果佢出口咬有冇咩建議可以阻止下佢"},{"pid":"1346369e945922b0abd458e9ec582747fca38ac8","tid":1912384,"uid":155431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:42:13.000Z","msg":"用玩具代替用手同佢玩<br />\n當佢當左你隻手係玩具<br />\n自然就會咬落你度<br />\n另外當隻貓咬你嘅時候<br />\n要大聲鬧佢 同埋打佢（輕手）<br />\n立即轉身離開<br />\n久而久之佢就知道咬人<br />\n係會俾人打同埋會受冷落"},{"pid":"aee314166a5540cfa8ce39bb9b38848b3ede588b","tid":1912384,"uid":289104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0f5b130527232ce17c03c8552240505201f44e82","tid":1912384,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"有冇貓貓圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:43:07.000Z","msg":"Sure<img src=\